Invocation Name: survivor history
des:
Ask about any season of Survivor. Find out who won, where it was filmed, and other cool facts.

Survivor History provides fun the whole family can enjoy and is guaranteed to make you a true Survivor fan.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Survivor History" or "Alexa, open Survivor History" to get started".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
